						               													<description>From the back of the box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For centuries, questions have persisted about the Hebrews flight from Egypt:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What route did the Hebrew tribes follow through the wilderness?&amp;#10;Where did God part the Red Sea?&amp;#10;How could so many people survive in a desert wasteland?&amp;#10;Where exactly is Mt. Sinai - the mountain upon which God descended to give Moses the ten commandments?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Explorer Bob Cornuke and his partner Larry Williams risked their very lives to answer these questions. Using the Bible as their road map, they embarked upon a death defying quest in search of ancient secrets hidden from the world for centuries.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Now you can experience their adventure first-hand as you, and up to three of your friends, embark on a perilous, thrill a minute, action filled expedition to search for Jabal Al Lawz...the real Mt. Sinai - the Lost Mountain of God!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Object of the Game:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Travel through Egypt and Saudi Arabia to Jabal Al Lawz in search of evidence supporting the story of the Exodus.&amp;#10;Use treasure you find along the way to buy your supplies and equipment such as water, first aid kits, rations, compass, gasoline, climbing rope, camera and night vision binoculars from Abdul's traveling caravan.&amp;#10;Contend with deadly creatures, the elements and each other in a winner-takes-all race to collect the photos and artifacts needed from Jabal Al Lawz to achieve your goal and escape from the mountain - alive!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Egypt deck (50 cards)&amp;#10;Saudi Arabia deck (50 cards)&amp;#10;Jabal Al Lawz deck (50 cards)&amp;#10;156 Supply cards&amp;#10;Abdul's Traveling Caravan&amp;#10;28 Photographic Evidence cards&amp;#10;Instruction Manual&amp;#10;Game Board&amp;#10;1 Die&amp;#10;4 Staff tokens&amp;#10;8 Tent tokens&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
